{
    "esm": "0.4.0",
    "metadata": {
        "name": "FastJXGEOSChemGasPhaseCoupling",
        "description": "FastJX photolysis model coupling to GEOSChemGasPhase reaction system. Maps the 12 photolysis rates computed by FastJX (j_H2O2, j_H2COa, j_H2COb, j_O3, j_O31D, j_NO2, j_NO3a, j_NO3b, j_N2O5, j_CH3OOH, j_ActAld, j_PAN) to the corresponding numbered photolysis-rate parameters in GEOSChemGasPhase (j_2, j_3, j_7, j_8, j_9, j_10, j_11, j_12, j_13, j_14, j_59, j_61). Implements the param_to_var coupling that replaces GEOSChemGasPhase's constant j-rate parameters with time-varying values computed by FastJX during simulation. Migrated from GasChem.jl@8c12c048 src/fastjx_couplings.jl:88 (esm-2jpi). Blocking gap gt-p3ep resolved by FastJX migration (esm-lnl6).",
        "tags": [
            "photolysis",
            "coupling",
            "gaschem",
            "fastjx",
            "geoschem",
            "param_to_var"
        ],
        "created": "2026-05-22T00:00:00Z",
        "authors": [
            "GasChem.jl contributors",
            "EarthSciModels migration (esm-2jpi)"
        ],
        "references": [
            {
                "citation": "Prather, M. J. (1992). Photolysis rates in correlated overlapping cloud fields: Cloud overlap and fraction. Journal of Geophysical Research: Atmospheres, 97(D9), 10103–10110. — Fast-JX photolysis algorithm and j-rate numbering scheme used in GEOS-Chem."
            },
            {
                "citation": "Bey, I., Jacob, D. J., Yantosca, R. M., Logan, J. A., Field, B. D., Fiore, A. M., … Schultz, M. G. (2001). Global modeling of tropospheric chemistry with assimilated meteorology: Model description and evaluation. Journal of Geophysical Research: Atmospheres, 106(D19), 23073–23095. — GEOS-Chem full-chemistry gas-phase mechanism and the j-rate parameter numbering (j_1..j_157+) used in GEOSChemGasPhase."
            }
        ]
    },
    "models": {
        "FastJX": {
            "coupletype": "FastJXCoupler",
            "reference": {
                "notes": "source_ref: GasChem.jl@8c12c048:src/fastjx_couplings.jl:88\n\nInterface stub declaring the 12 photolysis-rate outputs that the FastJX model provides for coupling to GEOSChemGasPhase. The full FastJX implementation with computed j-rates is at components/gaschem/fastjx/fastjx.esm (esm-lnl6).\n\nThe upstream GasChem.jl coupling (fastjx_couplings.jl) maps 64 GEOSChemGasPhase j-rate parameters to FastJX j-rates. Of these 64, the migrated FastJX.esm computes 12 (the core tropospheric photolysis rates). The remaining 52 — covering halogen species (j_ClNO3a/b, j_Cl2, j_HOCl, j_OClO, j_Cl2O2, j_ClO, j_BrO, j_BrNO3, j_HOBr, j_BrCl), halogenated hydrocarbons (j_OCS, j_CFCl3, j_CF2Cl2, j_F113..F115, j_CCl4, j_CH3Cl, j_MeCCl3, j_CH2Cl2, j_CHF2Cl, j_F123, j_F141b, j_F142b, j_CH3Br, j_H1211, j_H1301, j_H2402, j_CH2Br2, j_CHBr3, j_CH3I, j_CH3NO3), stratospheric species (j_O2, j_NO), and acid/nitrate species (j_HNO2, j_HNO3, j_HNO4), nitrate/organic carbonyls (j_MeVKa/b/c, j_MeAcr, j_GlyAld, j_MEKeto, j_PrAld, j_MGlyxl, j_Glyxla/b/c, j_Aceta/b) — are not included because they require FastJX spectral data beyond the 13 J-rates migrated in esm-lnl6. They will be added when a fuller FastJX migration covers those channels.\n\nVariable naming convention: j-rates are declared as `type: parameter` here (interface contract) even though FastJX computes them as `type: observed` internally. The `param_to_var` transform in the coupling entries declares that each GEOSChemGasPhase j_N parameter is replaced by the time-varying value from FastJX."
            },
            "variables": {
                "j_H2O2": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 9.153504300134295e-05,
                    "description": "H2O2 photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_H2O2 = (Σ_i F_i·σ_H2O2_i)·ϕ_H2O2 summed over 18 wavelength bins. Default is typical tropical noon (lat=0°, summer solstice noon, T=298 K, P=101325 Pa, H2O=450 ppb) from esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_H2COa": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 7.927569431680207e-05,
                    "description": "CH2O → CO + HO2 + H photolysis rate (radical channel) [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_H2COa = (Σ_i F_i·σ_H2COa_i)·ϕ_H2COa. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_H2COb": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 6.581696733212547e-05,
                    "description": "CH2O → CO + H2 photolysis rate (molecular channel) [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_H2COb = (Σ_i F_i·σ_H2COb_i)·ϕ_H2COb. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_O3": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.008115366636948307,
                    "description": "O3 → O2 + O(³P) photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_O3 = (Σ_i F_i·σ_O3_i)·ϕ_O3. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_O31D": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.006922533493689765,
                    "description": "O3 → O(¹D) + O2 photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_O31D = Σ_i F_i·σ_O3_i·ϕ_O31D_i(T) using temperature-dependent quantum yields. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_NO2": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.003903262349324107,
                    "description": "NO2 → NO + O(³P) photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_NO2 = (Σ_i F_i·σ_NO2_i)·ϕ_NO2. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_NO3a": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.2408349039976541,
                    "description": "NO3 → NO2 + O(³P) photolysis rate [s⁻¹] (branching ratio 0.886). Computed by FastJX as j_NO3a = (Σ_i F_i·σ_NO3_i)·ϕ_NO3·0.886. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_NO3b": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.030987786744619147,
                    "description": "NO3 → NO + O2 photolysis rate [s⁻¹] (branching ratio 0.114). Computed by FastJX as j_NO3b = (Σ_i F_i·σ_NO3_i)·ϕ_NO3·0.114. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_N2O5": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 0.000564451696257029,
                    "description": "N2O5 → NO3 + NO2 photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_N2O5 = (Σ_i F_i·σ_N2O5_i)·ϕ_N2O5. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_CH3OOH": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 4.960027768503218e-05,
                    "description": "CH3OOH (MP: methyl hydroperoxide) → HO2 + OH + CH2O photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_CH3OOH = (Σ_i F_i·σ_CH3OOH_i)·ϕ_CH3OOH. Corresponds to GEOSChemGasPhase species MP. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_ActAld": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 8.810269197300674e-05,
                    "description": "Acetaldehyde (ALD2: CH3CHO) → CO + MO2 + MCO3 + HO2 photolysis rate (radical channel, j_61 in GEOSChem KPP) [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_ActAld = (Σ_i F_i·σ_ActAld_i)·ϕ_ActAld. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                },
                "j_PAN": {
                    "type": "parameter",
                    "units": "1/s",
                    "default": 4.092859837238189e-05,
                    "description": "PAN → MCO3 + MO2 + NO3 + NO2 photolysis rate [s⁻¹]. Computed by FastJX as j_PAN = (Σ_i F_i·σ_PAN_i)·ϕ_PAN. Default: tropical noon, esm-lnl6 test suite."
                }
            },
            "equations": []
        }
    },
    "coupling": [
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_O3",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_2",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "O3 → O2 + O(³P) photolysis: FastJX.j_O3 → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_2 (R663 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_2=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_O31D",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_3",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "O3 → O(¹D) + O2 photolysis: FastJX.j_O31D → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_3 (R664 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_3=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_H2COa",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_7",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "CH2O → CO + HO2 + H photolysis (radical channel): FastJX.j_H2COa → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_7 (R669 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_7=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_H2COb",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_8",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "CH2O → CO + H2 photolysis (molecular channel): FastJX.j_H2COb → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_8 (R670 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_8=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_H2O2",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_9",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "H2O2 → OH + OH photolysis: FastJX.j_H2O2 → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_9 (R667 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_9=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_CH3OOH",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_10",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "MP (CH3OOH) → HO2 + OH + CH2O photolysis: FastJX.j_CH3OOH → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_10 (R668 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_10=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_NO2",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_11",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "NO2 → NO + O(³P) photolysis: FastJX.j_NO2 → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_11 (R666 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_11=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_NO3a",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_12",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "NO3 → NO2 + O(³P) photolysis (86.6% branch): FastJX.j_NO3a → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_12 (R675 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_12=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_NO3b",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_13",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "NO3 → NO + O2 photolysis (11.4% branch): FastJX.j_NO3b → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_13 (R676 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_13=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_N2O5",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_14",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "N2O5 → NO3 + NO2 photolysis: FastJX.j_N2O5 → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_14 (R677 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_14=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_PAN",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_59",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "PAN → MCO3 + MO2 + NO3 + NO2 photolysis: FastJX.j_PAN → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_59 (R680 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_59=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        },
        {
            "type": "variable_map",
            "from": "FastJX.j_ActAld",
            "to": "GEOSChemGasPhase.j_61",
            "transform": "param_to_var",
            "description": "ALD2 (CH3CHO) → CO + MO2 + MCO3 + HO2 photolysis (radical channel, j_61): FastJX.j_ActAld → GEOSChemGasPhase.j_61 (R678 in geoschem_fullchem.esm). Replaces the default constant j_61=0 with the FastJX time-varying rate."
        }
    ]
}
